{"name":"Rocket, Land Shark","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/ranged/projectile-strike-egg-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This rocket is a ranged weapon with a range of 60/120 feet. On impact, it deals 7d6 concussive damage to the target and to any creature or item 10 feet close to it. It requires a DC 12 save to half damage.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[warcraft5e.wc5e_mechanics.39Yud24y5rEAhlJp]{Earth (only)}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Rocket</strong></p>\n<p>Rockets are light ranged projectile weapons with a range of 60/120 feet that soar to the point of impact and then explode instantaneously. They deal no damage on impact, but explode when their fuse determines it (or upon impact, whichever applies). If modified with a fuse, the rocket instead embeds itself in the targeted area and explodes when the fuse determines it. A rocket that is launched beyond optimal range provides advantage to saving throws to half damage. If you target a creature with the rocket and succeed on the attack roll, they do not get to roll to halve damage, and suffer the full damage. The creatures in the blast radius are still entitled saving throws as normal. When a rocket reaches its maximum range, it explodes regardless of whether it reached its target or not. If it misses its target, however, it continues along the path without guidance, usually exploding at some other point (such as at the maximum range or upon impact with a wall). If launching a rocket on a target, the attack roll is the malfunction roll test, otherwise you must roll for malfunction as a separate d20 roll.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Wc5e - Core p. 222","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":320,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":60,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"ammo","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["7d6","concussive"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":12,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialR","baseItem":"generalExplosive","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"hvyplus":false,"lgt":true,"lod":false,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"bomb":false,"hvypl":false,"reloadpl":false,"reloadplus":false,"rocket":true,"mine":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"wc5e":{"type":"item","enhancement":"","mrmin":1,"mrmax":3}},"_id":"4kQGJZCejwpFE9EP"}
{"name":"Grenade, Plague Spreader","type":"weapon","img":"icons/skills/ranged/bomb-grenade-thrown-stars-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This grenade deals 4d6 concussive damage in a 10-foot sphere and creates a puff of noxious gas. A successful saving throw halves damage. Affected creatures must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or take 2d12 poison damage.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[warcraft5e.wc5e_mechanics.4SX6o4iNVGiV1OXL]{Weakened (3)}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Bomb</strong></p>\n<p>Bombs are thrown as light thrown weapons with a range of 30/60 feet. They deal no damage on impact, but explode when their fuse determines it (at the end of the user‘s turn, usually, see fuses below). A bomb that is thrown beyond optimal range provides advantage to saving throws to half damage. If you target a creature with the bomb as a ranged weapon attack and succeed on the attack roll, they do not get to roll to halve damage, and suffer the full damage. The creatures in the blast radius are still entitled saving throws as normal. If throwing a bomb on a target, the attack roll is the malfunction roll test, otherwise you must roll for malfunction as a separate d20 roll.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Wc5e - Core p. 222","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":320,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":30,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"ammo","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["4d6","concussive"],["2d12","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":12,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialR","baseItem":"ge