{"name":"Mine, Blasting","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/ball-spiked.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This mine triggers whenever any creature appears within its area of explosion. If a creature comes that close, it explodes, dealing 3d6 concussive damage to it and any creature within 10 feet. Creatures in range of the shockwave take an extra 1d6 points of damage and are pushed 10 feet away from the area of the explosion, as are unsecured objects. It requires a DC 12 save to half damage.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[warcraft5e.wc5e_mechanics.4SX6o4iNVGiV1OXL]{Weakened (2)}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Mine</strong></p>\n<p>Mines are explosive traps that explode when stepped on (unless modified with a fuse). A mine can be detected with a successful Spirit (Perception) check and disarmed with a successful Agility (Thieves‘ Tools) check against the Device save DC, and is treated as a trap. The mine must pass a successful malfunction roll test.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Wc5e - Core p. 222","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":80,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"ammo","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["6d6","arcane"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":12,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialR","baseItem":"generalExplosive","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"hvyplus":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,