{"name":"Mine, Fel Iron","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/ball-spiked.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This mine triggers whenever any creature appears within its area of explosion. If a creature comes that close, it explodes, dealing 8d6 concussive damage to it and any creature within 10 feet. It requires a DC 12 save to half damage.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[warcraft5e.wc5e_mechanics.0kkX8fLDVucLKRE4]{Reliable Device} @Compendium[warcraft5e.wc5e_mechanics.4SX6o4iNVGiV1OXL]{Weakened}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Mine</strong></p>\n<p>Mines are explosive traps that explode when stepped on (unless modified with a fuse). A mine can be detected with a successful Spirit (Perception) check and disarmed with a successful Agility (Thieves‘ Tools) check against the Device save DC, and is treated as a trap. The mine must pass a successful malfunction roll test.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Wc5e - Core p. 222","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":1280,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"ammo","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["8d6","arcane"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialR","baseItem":"generalExplosive","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"hvyplus":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"bomb":false,"hvypl":false,"reloadpl":false,"reloadplus":false,"rocket":fa